{"tid":1367414,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)新美國總領事上場!","createTime":"2019-07-26T08:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T08:56:29.000Z","uid":164606,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"591a392bc76d6b571ec544f07fabef167349721f","tid":1367414,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"今日係我第一日番到領事館，好榮幸見到一班響領事館服務咗好耐嘅員工！- 總領事史墨客<br />\n<br />\nOn my first day in Hong Kong, I was honored to be met by a group of our longest-serving employees upon my arrival at the Consulate. - HS<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ne2MMyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNe2MMyW.jpg&h=412980d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSir This Way<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd848d16ef15eaf70f95f46f1270491233acd078","tid":1367414,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />準備好帶路未?"},{"pid":"d0cee4c4f3730b3ed488c6b47a0f80d013c20a92","tid":1367414,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"Goodest timing<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cccaecbdf38fbf47bda7d31916355134c8bb84ab","tid":1367414,"uid":164606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:54:31.000Z","msg":"墨客是職業外交官，之前在美國國務院出任主管中國事務處的副助理國務卿，曾經出任美國駐上海總領事和中國及蒙古事務處處長等，本身識中文，他另一個為人熟識之處是他的同性戀取向，他的配偶是台灣人呂英宗（ Eric Lu）。<br />\n<br />\n2016年，當時在任美國駐上海總領事的史墨客，微博貼出他與同姓伴侶呂英宗的結婚照，他表示是時候與大家分享這個好消息。他表示呂英宗是他多年的伴侶，兩人選在美國三藩市結婚，也強調三藩市在LGBT平權運動上的地位舉足輕重。"},{"pid":"cc1e71c410561f68859b93b0b5fcb474059faa4c","tid":1367414,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"史墨客就任駐港澳總領事正值香港&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;近年不斷受北京侵蝕，而港府近期強行推動逃犯條例修訂案引發香港社會激烈對立之際。修訂案一旦通過，可允許將港人引渡到沒有任何司法獨立的中國大陸，而美國也將會重新審議給予香港的特殊優惠待遇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc39f26e20eb7c7aedbabb173d40ec2259c516f7","tid":1367414,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:55:23.000Z","msg":"Spirit of the USA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b075420149281ec4c32ee091f0bcf3e65e7bb02b","tid":1367414,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:56:29.000Z","msg":"快點派軍吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}